    "body": "I'm not sure I'm buying what you're selling here, @domenkozar. starship has a Node.js module and a Bun module. They're both JavaScript runtimes.\n\nWhen I enter a project that has a `flake.nix` I want starship to let me know about that, so that I don't even need to list the files to know that I can run `nix develop`. And if a project has a `devenv.nix` file, then I'd like starship to inform me of that, so that I don't have to list the files to know that I can run `devenv shell`.",
